description: AMUNDI MSCI EM ASIA UCITS ETF seeks to replicate as closely as possible the performance of the MSCI Emerging Markets Asia Index, net dividends reinvested (Net Return), calculated in US Dollars and converted in euro, whether the trend is rising or falling. This ETF enables investors to benefit from an exposure to the leading stocks from Asian equity emerging markets, with a single transaction. For further information, please also refer to the fund prospectus.
name: Amundi MSCI Em Asia UCITS ETF - EUR (C)
